  <summary date="2022-08-30T17:09:04Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Beagle Brigade Act of 2022

This bill provides statutory authority for the National Detector Dog Training Center that is operated by the Animal and Plant Health Inspection Service of the Department of Agriculture. The center trains dogs to inspect passenger baggage, cargo, mailed packages, and vehicles to detect foreign pests and diseases that threaten domestic agriculture and natural resources.</summary>
